{"tid":2377926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國富時指數UK's FTSE Russell將中海油移除","createTime":"2021-01-24T04:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T04:56:57.000Z","uid":294518,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c148d2b13bad6ae0625b84eb0f1f52feb04965e7","tid":2377926,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:53:48.000Z","msg":"英國富時指數將中海油移除<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/siladityaray/2021/01/22/uks-ftse-russell-removes-chinas-cnooc-from-indexes-to-comply-with-trump-ban/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fsiladityaray%2F2021%2F01%2F22%2Fuks-ftse-russell-removes-chinas-cnooc-from-indexes-to-comply-with-trump-ban%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Tap4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=9f2d0827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/siladityaray/2021/01/22/uks-ftse-russell-removes-chinas-cnooc-from-indexes-to-comply-with-trump-ban/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNDi4M9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNDi4M9.png&h=56cf9aad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb0f883af4ab7a8d79af7b9f4f4518fee6eb9ea8","tid":2377926,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"英國富時羅素指數根據川普政府的禁令移除中海油<br />\n<br />\n倫敦證卷交易所旗下的指數提供商富時羅素指數將會從其全球和中國頂級企業指數中移除中共國石油天然氣公司中海油，該指數提供商在周五宣布這項舉措，這是直接受川普政府禁止美國投資中共黑名單企業的禁令影響而做出的。"},{"pid":"d6b2fbb28e2eb518b4575cc392dec991046bbfc9","tid":2377926,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"關鍵事實<br />\n<br />\n在香港上市的中海油將會被富時全球指數和富時中國A50指數移除，報導稱1月27日開始執行。<br />\n<br />\n該聲明在香港工作時間公開，中海油在港交所股價下滑5.5%。"},{"pid":"b0a4048e90b3c7389c2260b8382170078347e469","tid":2377926,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"背景<br />\n去年11月，美國前總統川普簽署行政命令，禁止美國人投資美國政府認定為中共軍方、情報部門和安全部門的公司。該禁令禁止這些公司的股票交易，1月11日開執行，現持股的投資者可以到今年11月前考慮撤出投資。在川普在任最後一周，川普政府將中海油和小米加入貿易黑名單。在一系列的反復之後，紐約證交所最終根據行政命令摘牌了中國移動、中國聯通和中國電信的美國股份。"}]}